*  2001   &amp;ndash; [[Dorothy Tutin]], English actress (b. 1930)
*[[2002]] &amp;ndash; [[Edsger W. Dijkstra]], Dutch computer scientist (b. 1930)
*[[2004]] &amp;ndash; [[Rick James]], American singer-songwriter, musician, and producer ([[The Mynah Birds]]) (b. 1948)
*[[2005]] &amp;ndash; [[Keter Betts]], American bassist (b. 1928)
*  2005   &amp;ndash; [[Robin Cook]], Scottish politician (b. 1946)
*  2005   &amp;ndash; [[Ibrahim Ferrer]], Cuban singer ([[Buena Vista Social Club]]) (b. 1927)
*[[2007]] &amp;ndash; [[Heinz Barth]], German [[SS]] officer (b. 1920)
*  2007   &amp;ndash; [[Zsolt Daczi]], Hungarian guitarist ([[Bikini (Hungarian band)|Bikini]]) (b. 1969)
*[[2008]] &amp;ndash; [[Angelos Kitsos]], Greek lawyer, scriptwriter, and author (b. 1934)
*[[2009]] &amp;ndash; [[Riccardo Cassin]], Italian mountaineer (b. 1909)
*  2009   &amp;ndash; [[Willy DeVille]],  American singer-songwriter and guitarist ([[Mink DeVille]]) (b. 1950)
*  2009   &amp;ndash; [[John Hughes (filmmaker)|John Hughes]],  American director, screenwriter, and producer (b. 1950)
*  2009   &amp;ndash; [[W. S. Rendra]], Indonesian poet and playwright (b. 1935)
*[[2011]] &amp;ndash; [[Fe del Mundo]], Filipino pediatrician (b. 1911)
*[[2012]] &amp;ndash; [[Richard Cragun]], American ballet dancer (b. 1944)
